

# Get Involved


## IRC

You can find us at the #apoc channel on irc.freenode.net. 


## Mailing list

For general discussion, get subscribed to the [[apoc mailing list|http://lists.freedesktop.org/mailman/listinfo/apoc]]. 

You can also browse the [[mailing list archives|http://lists.freedesktop.org/archives/apoc/]] to read about previous topics. 


## Bugs!

Please, feel free to report bugs and patches to our [[bugzilla|https://bugs.freedesktop.org/]] component. 


## Git repository

You can browse the source code in the freedesktop.org [[git web interface|http://gitweb.freedesktop.org/]]. 


## Contributions

If you are interested in contributing to the project with code or documentation, we encourage you to read the [[contributor's guide|GettingInvolved/ContributionsGuide]]. 
